OL,6,FBritish Steel could be renationalised
OL,7,Funder plans reportedly being
OL,8,Fconsidered by the Government amid
OL,9,Funcertainty about the company's future.
OL,11,FMinisters have been locked in talks
OL,12,Fwith the company's Chinese owners,
OL,13,FJingye, over a potential rescue plan
OL,14,Ffor its Scunthorpe plant.
OL,16,FBritish Steel announced it would close
OL,17,Fits blast furnaces in Scunthorpe last
OL,18,Fyear, replacing them with a less
OL,19,Fpolluting electric arc furnace if it
OL,20,Freceived "appropriate support" from
OL,21,Fthe Government.
