OL,6,F"Leaving domestic production to the
OL,7,Fwhims of the open market is sheer
OL,8,Ffolly. Rather than forking out
OL,9,Fbillions of taxpayer cash to reward
OL,10,Fprivate sector failure, the money
OL,11,Fshould be used to renationalise our
OL,12,Fonce proud steel sector."
OL,14,FUnite's general secretary, Sharon
OL,15,FGraham, argued that steel should be
OL,16,Fdesignated as "critical
OL,17,Finfrastructure" and accused previous
