OL,6,FIn Government, Labour announced a #500
OL,7,Fmillion package to support Tata's
OL,8,Fsteelworks in Port Talbot make the
OL,9,Ftransition to low-carbon steel
OL,10,Fproduction, but the closure of blast
OL,11,Ffurnaces at the plant still brought
OL,12,Fthe loss of almost 2,000 jobs.
OL,14,FAbout 4,000 people work at British
OL,15,FSteel's Scunthorpe plant, which is now
OL,16,Fthe only facility making primary steel
OL,17,Fin the UK.
